{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01MeKV6oUjVtUtGjoB7QZgeo","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Everything is complete and working. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Problem:** MinIO had no Kubernetes Service (the `minio-init` job failed because DNS for `minio.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local` didn't exist), and the `es-secure-settings` secret and `repository-s3` plugin were missing.\n\n**Steps taken:**\n\n1. **Created the MinIO Service** — exposed `minio.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local:9000` so ES nodes could reach it.\n\n2. **Created `es-secure-settings` Secret** — stored `s3.client.default.access_key` and `s3.client.default.secret_key` (both `minioadmin`) as Kubernetes secret keys.\n\n3. **Installed `repository-s3` plugin** on all 3 pods directly, then **patched the StatefulSet** with two init containers:\n   - `install-s3-plugin`: downloads and installs the plugin into a shared `emptyDir` volume mounted at `/usr/share/elasticsearch/plugins`\n   - `setup-keystore`: reads credentials from the `es-secure-settings` secret volume, populates a fresh keystore, and writes it to a shared `emptyDir` mounted at the keystore path — **credentials never touch `elasticsearch.yml` or env vars**\n\n4. **Rolled the StatefulSet** — all 3 pods restarted with the plugin active and keystore loaded from the secret.\n\n5. **Created the `es-backups` bucket** in MinIO (the init job had failed earlier).\n\n6. **Registered `minio-repo`** snapshot repository pointing at `minio.elasticsearch.svc.cluster.local:9000`.\n\n7. **Created `snapshot-1`** — completed with `state: SUCCESS`, 2 shards snapshotted, 0 failures."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":539,"cache_read_input_tokens":56622,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":539},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd909928-9b75-4fc5-8e2c-3625ffbaced2","uuid":"74e18020-78c5-42db-8c04-e3747e486c25","request_id":"req_011CcP8jESfJU3Gm45F9Kf5h"}
